  {
    "id": "1780646670294",
    "name": "翔泰陶瓷",
    "nameEn": "Xiangtai Ceramics",
    "category": "瓷砖建材",
    "categoryEn": "Ceramic tiles and building materials",
    "location": "肇庆",
    "locationEn": "Zhaoqing",
    "description": "    我们是集研发、智造、销售为一体的现代化大中型墙地砖生产企业，全线引进国际化智能生产设备，配备300m 超长节能窑炉、7200T 大吨位数控压机、高端湿法球磨机、宽幅同步智能输送系统等成套智能化产线\n    工厂统筹全品类瓷砖量产，覆盖通体地砖、墙面砖、仿大理石板材、装饰罗马柱等中高端全系产品，依托全品类配套优势，一站式输出家装、工装整装配套解决方案\n    企业先后取得3C 强制性产品认证、ISO9001 质量管理体系、ISO14001 环境管理体系、GB/T28001 职业健康安全管理体系多项权威认证\n    深耕绿色智造，环保硬件投入超 1000 万元，年度环保运维支出 700 万元以上，合规稳定承接地产、酒店大批量集采订单",
    "descriptionEn": "    We are a modern medium-to-large sized wall and floor tile manufacturer integrating R&D, intelligent manufacturing and sales. We have introduced full-range internationally sourced intelligent production equipment, including complete intelligent production lines equipped with an ultra-long 300-meter energy-saving kiln, 7200-ton large-tonnage numerical control presses, high-end wet ball mills, wide-format synchronous intelligent conveying systems and other supporting facilities.\n\n    Our factory arranges mass production of a full spectrum of ceramic tiles, covering mid-to-high-end full-range products such as full-body floor tiles, wall tiles, imitation marble slabs and decorative Roman columns. Leveraging our full-product matching advantages, we provide one-stop complete supporting solutions for residential decoration and commercial construction projects.\n\n    The enterprise has successively obtained multiple authoritative certifications including China Compulsory Certification (3C), ISO9001 Quality Management System Certification, ISO14001 Environmental Management System Certification and GB/T28001 Occupational Health and Safety Management System Certification.\n\n    Committed to green intelligent manufacturing, we have invested over 10 million RMB in environmental protection hardware, with annual environmental protection operation and maintenance expenses exceeding 7 million RMB, enabling us to legally and steadily undertake bulk centralized procurement orders from real estate developers and hotels.",
